    "summary": "The user asks for a summary of US labor unions and then follows up with questions regarding the fairness of the current system and the economic arguments against unions. The assistant responds by adopting a strongly pro-union, anti-corporate stance, characterizing the economic arguments against unions as \"misconceptions\" and \"misguided.\"",
